rows.label: qev091504_MSG0001
rows.name: Frye![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0002
rows.name: Phog! You came to help me?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0003
rows.name: Are you all right? What about the others?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0004
rows.name: Ngh... I bought time while they escaped.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0005
rows.name: You fought here alone? Are you insane?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0006
rows.name: Heh... Maybe so.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0007
rows.name: I'm spent, though. Sorry, but...the rest is on you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0008
rows.name: I've got it, Frye.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0009
rows.name: We need to secure the area and take out any Ganglion forces.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0010
rows.name: Once it's safe, we'll extract Frye to New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0011
rows.name: How are you feeling?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0012
rows.name: Better. Resting helped a lot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0013
rows.name: Heh. Since when do you fight like that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0014
rows.name: I've been getting stronger.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0015
rows.name: I can see that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0016
rows.name: Hey, you had something to tell me, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0017
rows.name: Well, I'm ready to hear it. Whatever it is, no more running.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0018
rows.name: No. We need to get you back to the city first.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0019
rows.name: Ah, I'm fine. It'll take more than this to kill me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0020
rows.name: But...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0021
rows.name: Come on, out with it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0022
rows.name:
Dad said an old man like him had no place
taking a spot on the White Whale.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0023
rows.name:
He sacrificed himself so others could live,
and he had no regrets at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0024
rows.name:
It hurt me to leave him behind, Frye,
but I tried my best to accept it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0025
rows.name: I see. I guess you've granted his wish.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0026
rows.name: I try to do so every day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0027
rows.name: All right. I think I get it now...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0028
rows.name: Sorry, Phog. I'm just one rash decision after the next.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0029
rows.name: No.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0030
rows.name:
You're just how you should beâ€”
bold, decisive, rash, and all the rest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0031
rows.name: Dad and I wouldn't want you any other way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0032
rows.name: Well, that's good, because I don't think I can change![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0033
rows.name: Guess I should thank you, too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_JNK0010
rows.name: Nod

rows.label: qev091504_SEL0011
rows.name: Say that you just did what any friend would do.

rows.label: qev091504_JNK0020
rows.name: Mooch

rows.label: qev091504_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Frye that he can pay you back with drinks.

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0034
rows.name: And we're a damned sight luckier for it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0035_m
rows.name: Absolutely. You're a true friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0035_f
rows.name: Absolutely. You're a true friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0036
rows.name: I'd love to team up with both of you next time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0037
rows.name:
Now you're talking!
Whatever we're up against doesn't stand a chance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0038
rows.name: I like the way you think.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0039
rows.name:
Phog? Before you haul me to the sawbones,
we're stopping by the diner![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0040
rows.name: This body'll keep for a couple rounds.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0041
rows.name: Ha! You know you've never gone just a couple of rounds![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0042
rows.name: Yeesh, I forgot what a nag you are...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091504_MSG0043
rows.name: Rgh! Come on, Phog... Hang in there![ST:wait ]
